description:
Today Ollie and Jake venture into the mines of Embergard, hoping to catch a glimpse of the new Warhammer Underworlds core set! 

Will they be lost eternally in the winding, unending depths, never to see the light of day again, or will they paint a fighter from each Warband and have a great time doing it?

Let's find out!
